OL,3,CPaws on the cobbles: More than 200
OL,4,Cdogs visit Coronation Street
OL,6,FThe most famous street on television
OL,7,Fsaw a different kind of "ruff" drama
OL,8,Fas more than 200 dogs took over the
OL,9,Ffamous Coronation Street cobbles.
OL,11,FFor the first time ever, the studio in
OL,12,FMedia City in Salford opened its gates
OL,13,Fto a flurry of four-legged fans, with
OL,14,Fmany owners dressing their pets up to
OL,15,Fmark the historic occasion.
OL,17,FAll dog tickets sold for the special
OL,18,Fwalk raised money for Dogs Trust, the
OL,19,FUK's largest dog welfare charity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
