OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776096668
OL,3,CPaws on the cobbles: More than 200
OL,4,Cdogs visit Coronation Street
OL,6,FWeatherfield's police station saw pugs
OL,7,FLilly and Lulu dressed as police
OL,8,Fofficers and further down the street,
OL,9,Fowner Brad Wood posed with his dog
OL,10,FBobby, a French bulldog, outside The
OL,11,FKabin newsagent.
OL,13,FThe soap street is currently home to
OL,14,Fthe Platt family dog, which is named
OL,15,FDavid after its owner.
OL,17,FOther canine characters have included
OL,18,FEvelyn Plummer's greyhound Cerberus,
OL,19,FChesney Brown's great dane Schmeichel
OL,20,Fand Maria Connor's labrador Ozzy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
