OL,3,CPaws on the cobbles: More than 200
OL,4,Cdogs visit Coronation Street
OL,6,FFans enjoyed walking their dogs on the
OL,7,Fcobbles throughout the day, and owner
OL,8,FAnnie Palmas dressed her dogs ` Joey
OL,9,Fand Jessie ` in matching blue collars
OL,10,Fto commemorate the occasion.
OL,12,FTillie, a spaniel, and Dollie, a
OL,13,Fchihuahua, could be seen posing for
OL,14,Fpictures outside the street's famous
OL,15,FThe Rovers Return Inn.
